---
import { FontAwesomeIcon } from '@fortawesome/react-fontawesome';
import {
  faGift,
  faUserSlash,
  faShieldHalved,
  faCheck,
  faFileArrowDown,
  faBolt,
  faLink,
  faWifi,
  faAddressCard,
  faEnvelope,
  faComment,
  faPhone,
  faFileLines,
  faUtensils,
  faBriefcase,
  faTicket,
  faBox,
  faMobileScreenButton,
} from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons';
---

<section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 mt-12 border-t border-(--color-border)">
  {/* Why Choose Section */}
  <div class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-(--color-text-primary) mb-6 text-center">
      Why Choose Our QR Code Generator?
    </h2>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-(--color-background) p-6 rounded-lg border border-(--color-border) hover:border-blue-300 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-(--color-text-primary) mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
          <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faGift} className="text-blue-600 h-5 w-5" aria-hidden="true" />
          Completely Free
        </h3>
        <p class="text-(--color-text-secondary) leading-relaxed text-justify">
          No hidden costs, no premium tiers, and no feature limits. Every feature 
          is available to everyone, forever. Create unlimited QR codes without 
          paying a cent.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-(--color-background) p-6 rounded-lg border border-(--color-border) hover:border-blue-300 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-(--color-text-primary) mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
          <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faUserSlash} className="text-blue-600 h-5 w-5" aria-hidden="true" />
          No Signup Required
        </h3>
        <p class="text-(--color-text-secondary) leading-relaxed text-justify">
          Start generating QR codes immediately. No email verification, no password 
          creation, no personal information needed. Just visit the site and create 
          your QR code.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-(--color-background) p-6 rounded-lg border border-(--color-border) hover:border-blue-300 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-(--color-text-primary) mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
          <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faShieldHalved} className="text-blue-600 h-5 w-5" aria-hidden="true" />
          100% Private
        </h3>
        <p class="text-(--color-text-secondary) leading-relaxed text-justify">
          Your data never leaves your browser. All QR code generation happens
          client-side using JavaScript. We don't see, store, or transmit any 
          of the information you enter.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-(--color-background) p-6 rounded-lg border border-(--color-border) hover:border-blue-300 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-(--color-text-primary) mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
          <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faCheck} className="text-blue-600 h-5 w-5" aria-hidden="true" />
          No Watermarks
        </h3>
        <p class="text-(--color-text-secondary) leading-relaxed text-justify">
          Clean, professional QR codes with no branding or watermarks. Your QR 
          codes contain only the data you input - perfect for business and 
          professional use.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-(--color-background) p-6 rounded-lg border border-(--color-border) hover:border-blue-300 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-(--color-text-primary) mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
          <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faFileArrowDown} className="text-blue-600 h-5 w-5" aria-hidden="true" />
          Multiple Formats
        </h3>
        <p class="text-(--color-text-secondary) leading-relaxed text-justify">
          Download QR codes as PNG, SVG, JPG, or PDF. Choose from multiple 
          resolutions (256px to 2048px) to match your specific needs, from web 
          use to large format printing.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-(--color-background) p-6 rounded-lg border border-(--color-border) hover:border-blue-300 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-(--color-text-primary) mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
          <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faBolt} className="text-blue-600 h-5 w-5" aria-hidden="true" />
          Instant Generation
        </h3>
        <p class="text-(--color-text-secondary) leading-relaxed text-justify">
          QR codes generate in real-time as you type. See your QR code update 
          instantly and download immediately. No waiting, no processing delays.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {/* Supported Types Section */}
  <div class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-(--color-text-primary) mb-6 text-center">
      Supported QR Code Types
    </h2>
    
    <p class="text-lg text-(--color-text-secondary) mb-6 leading-relaxed text-justify">
      Our QR code generator supports all the most popular QR code types for both 
      personal and business use. Each type is optimized to work with standard QR 
      code readers on iOS and Android devices.
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <div class="bg-linear-to-r from-blue-50 to-(--color-background) dark:from-blue-950/20 dark:to-(--color-background) p-6 rounded-lg border border-blue-100 dark:border-blue-900/30">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-(--color-text-primary) mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
          <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faLink} className="text-blue-600 h-5 w-5" aria-hidden="true" />
          URL / Website QR Codes
        </h3>
        <p class="text-(--color-text-secondary) leading-relaxed text-justify">
          Create QR codes that link directly to any website. Perfect for marketing 
          campaigns, business cards, product packaging, or anywhere you want to drive 
          traffic to your website. When scanned, users are taken directly to your URL.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-linear-to-r from-blue-50 to-(--color-background) dark:from-blue-950/20 dark:to-(--color-background) p-6 rounded-lg border border-blue-100 dark:border-blue-900/30">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-(--color-text-primary) mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
          <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faWifi} className="text-blue-600 h-5 w-5" aria-hidden="true" />
          WiFi QR Codes
        </h3>
        <p class="text-(--color-text-secondary) leading-relaxed text-justify">
          Share WiFi network credentials instantly. Customers and guests can connect 
          to your network by simply scanning the QR code - no need to manually type 
          complex passwords. Supports WPA, WPA2, and WEP encryption.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-linear-to-r from-blue-50 to-(--color-background) dark:from-blue-950/20 dark:to-(--color-background) p-6 rounded-lg border border-blue-100 dark:border-blue-900/30">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-(--color-text-primary) mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
          <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faAddressCard} className="text-blue-600 h-5 w-5" aria-hidden="true" />
          vCard / Contact QR Codes
        </h3>
        <p class="text-(--color-text-secondary) leading-relaxed text-justify">
          Create digital business cards that can be scanned and saved directly to 
          contacts. Include name, phone number, email, company, job title, address, 
          and website. Perfect for networking events and professional use.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-linear-to-r from-blue-50 to-(--color-background) dark:from-blue-950/20 dark:to-(--color-background) p-6 rounded-lg border border-blue-100 dark:border-blue-900/30">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-(--color-text-primary) mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
          <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faEnvelope} className="text-blue-600 h-5 w-5" aria-hidden="true" />
          Email QR Codes
        </h3>
        <p class="text-(--color-text-secondary) leading-relaxed text-justify">
          Generate QR codes that open a new email with pre-filled recipient, subject, 
          and message body. Great for customer support, feedback forms, or making it 
          easy for people to contact you.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-linear-to-r from-blue-50 to-(--color-background) dark:from-blue-950/20 dark:to-(--color-background) p-6 rounded-lg border border-blue-100 dark:border-blue-900/30">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-(--color-text-primary) mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
          <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faComment} className="text-blue-600 h-5 w-5" aria-hidden="true" />
          SMS / Text Message QR Codes
        </h3>
        <p class="text-(--color-text-secondary) leading-relaxed text-justify">
          Create QR codes that open a text message with a pre-filled phone number and 
          message. Perfect for marketing campaigns, contest entries, or quick customer 
          responses.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-linear-to-r from-blue-50 to-(--color-background) dark:from-blue-950/20 dark:to-(--color-background) p-6 rounded-lg border border-blue-100 dark:border-blue-900/30">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-(--color-text-primary) mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
          <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faPhone} className="text-blue-600 h-5 w-5" aria-hidden="true" />
          Phone Number QR Codes
        </h3>
        <p class="text-(--color-text-secondary) leading-relaxed text-justify">
          Generate QR codes that initiate a phone call when scanned. Perfect for
          customer service, business cards, or any situation where you want to make it 
          easy for people to call you.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-linear-to-r from-blue-50 to-(--color-background) dark:from-blue-950/20 dark:to-(--color-background) p-6 rounded-lg border border-blue-100 dark:border-blue-900/30">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-(--color-text-primary) mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
          <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faFileLines} className="text-blue-600 h-5 w-5" aria-hidden="true" />
          Plain Text QR Codes
        </h3>
        <p class="text-(--color-text-secondary) leading-relaxed text-justify">
          Encode any text content into a QR code. Great for serial numbers, codes,
          instructions, or any information you want to share in a scannable format.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {/* How It Works Section */}
  <div class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-(--color-text-primary) mb-6 text-center">
      How It Works
    </h2>
    
    <p class="text-lg text-(--color-text-secondary) mb-8 leading-relaxed text-justify">
      Creating QR codes with our generator is simple and takes just a few seconds. 
      Follow these easy steps to create your QR code:
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xl">
          1
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-(--color-text-primary) mb-2">
            Select Your QR Code Type
          </h3>
          <p class="text-(--color-text-secondary) leading-relaxed text-justify">
            Choose from URL, WiFi, vCard, Email, SMS, Phone, or Text. Each type 
            has its own specialized form fields optimized for that data type.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xl">
          2
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-(--color-text-primary) mb-2">
            Enter Your Information
          </h3>
          <p class="text-(--color-text-secondary) leading-relaxed text-justify">
            Fill in the form fields with your data. For example, enter your website 
            URL, WiFi credentials, contact information, or whatever content you want 
            to encode in the QR code.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xl">
          3
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-(--color-text-primary) mb-2">
            Watch Your QR Code Generate
          </h3>
          <p class="text-(--color-text-secondary) leading-relaxed text-justify">
            Your QR code generates automatically in real-time as you type. You'll 
            see the QR code update instantly in the preview area. All processing 
            happens locally in your browser - your data never leaves your device.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xl">
          4
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-(--color-text-primary) mb-2">
            Download Your QR Code
          </h3>
          <p class="text-(--color-text-secondary) leading-relaxed text-justify">
            Choose your preferred format (PNG, SVG, JPG, or PDF) and resolution. 
            Click the download button and your QR code is immediately saved to your 
            device. Use it in print materials, websites, presentations, or anywhere 
            else you need it.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 p-6 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-950/20 border border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-900/30 rounded-lg">
      <p class="text-blue-950 dark:text-blue-200 leading-relaxed">
        <strong class="text-blue-950 dark:text-blue-100">Pro Tip:</strong> Always test your QR 
        code before printing or sharing widely. Scan it with your phone's camera 
        app to make sure it leads to the correct destination and works as expected.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  {/* Use Cases Section */}
  <div class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-(--color-text-primary) mb-6 text-center">
      Popular Use Cases
    </h2>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="text-center p-6">
        <div class="text-4xl mb-3 flex justify-center">
          <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faUtensils} className="text-blue-600 h-8 w-8" aria-hidden="true" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-(--color-text-primary) mb-2">
          Restaurant Menus
        </h3>
        <p class="text-(--color-text-secondary) text-sm">
          Create contactless digital menus that customers can access by scanning
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center p-6">
        <div class="text-4xl mb-3 flex justify-center">
          <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faBriefcase} className="text-blue-600 h-8 w-8" aria-hidden="true" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-(--color-text-primary) mb-2">
          Business Cards
        </h3>
        <p class="text-(--color-text-secondary) text-sm">
          Add vCard QR codes to share contact info instantly at networking events
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center p-6">
        <div class="text-4xl mb-3 flex justify-center">
          <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faTicket} className="text-blue-600 h-8 w-8" aria-hidden="true" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-(--color-text-primary) mb-2">
          Event Tickets
        </h3>
        <p class="text-(--color-text-secondary) text-sm">
          Generate QR codes for event registration, check-in, and information
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center p-6">
        <div class="text-4xl mb-3 flex justify-center">
          <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faBox} className="text-blue-600 h-8 w-8" aria-hidden="true" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-(--color-text-primary) mb-2">
          Product Packaging
        </h3>
        <p class="text-(--color-text-secondary) text-sm">
          Link to product info, instructions, or warranty registration pages
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center p-6">
        <div class="text-4xl mb-3 flex justify-center">
          <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faMobileScreenButton} className="text-blue-600 h-8 w-8" aria-hidden="true" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-(--color-text-primary) mb-2">
          App Downloads
        </h3>
        <p class="text-(--color-text-secondary) text-sm">
          Direct users to your app on the App Store or Google Play
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center p-6">
        <div class="text-4xl mb-3 flex justify-center">
          <FontAwesomeIcon icon={faWifi} className="text-blue-600 h-8 w-8" aria-hidden="true" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-(--color-text-primary) mb-2">
          Guest WiFi
        </h3>
        <p class="text-(--color-text-secondary) text-sm">
          Let visitors connect to your WiFi network without typing passwords
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {/* FAQ Section */}
  <div class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-(--color-text-primary) mb-6 text-center">
      Frequently Asked Questions
    </h2>
    
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-(--color-text-primary) mb-2">
          Are QR codes really free?
        </h3>
        <p class="text-(--color-text-secondary) leading-relaxed text-justify">
          Yes! Our QR code generator is completely free with no hidden costs, 
          limits, or premium features. Create as many QR codes as you need, 
          whenever you need them.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-(--color-text-primary) mb-2">
          Do QR codes expire?
        </h3>
        <p class="text-(--color-text-secondary) leading-relaxed text-justify">
          No, QR codes generated with our tool never expire. The QR code contains 
          your data directly - it's not a redirect or short link that could expire. 
          Your QR code will work forever.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-(--color-text-primary) mb-2">
          Can I use these QR codes commercially?
        </h3>
        <p class="text-(--color-text-secondary) leading-relaxed text-justify">
          Absolutely! You can use QR codes generated with our tool for any purpose, 
          including commercial use. There are no restrictions or licensing fees.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-(--color-text-primary) mb-2">
          What format should I use for printing?
        </h3>
        <p class="text-(--color-text-secondary) leading-relaxed text-justify">
          For professional printing, we recommend SVG format as it's vector-based 
          and scales to any size without losing quality. For large format printing, 
          use PNG at 2048px or higher. PDF is also great for print materials.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-(--color-text-primary) mb-2">
          Is my data really private?
        </h3>
        <p class="text-(--color-text-secondary) leading-relaxed text-justify">
          Yes! All QR code generation happens entirely in your web browser using 
          client-side JavaScript. Your data is never transmitted to our servers or 
          any third party. Once you close the browser tab, your data is gone.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-(--color-text-primary) mb-2">
          What's the maximum amount of data I can encode?
        </h3>
        <p class="text-(--color-text-secondary) leading-relaxed text-justify">
          QR codes can theoretically hold up to 4,296 alphanumeric characters, but 
          we recommend keeping your data concise. Smaller amounts of data create 
          simpler QR codes that are easier to scan reliably.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
